description:
&lt;p&gt;*Pending AfC Banding*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced Senior Moving and Handling Advisor to join our established team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will support the Trust&#39;s Moving and Handling Lead to provide professional advice, training and support services across the Royal Shrewsbury Hospital and The Princess Royal Hospital, Telford and all other sites across Shropshire where Trust staff work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A nationally recognised qualification in Safer People Handling and Manual Handling is essential, as is a recognised training qualification and experience in delivering moving and handling training and advisory services in an acute setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For informal enquiries please contact Hilary Morton, Moving and Handling Lead on 01952 641222 x 4769 or at hilary.morton1@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that this post&#39;s banding is subject to Agenda for Change evaluation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameHilary MortonJob titleMoving and Handling LeadEmail addresshilary.morton1@nhs.netTelephone number01952 641222 x4769&lt;/p&gt;
